column2: SELECT ALL m.OBJID AS akari_ID, m.RA AS akari_ra, m.DEC AS akari_dec, o.modelMag_u AS model_u, o.psfMag_u AS psf_u, o.fiberMag_u AS fiber_u, o.petroMag_u AS petro_u, o.dered_u AS dered_u into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.akari1# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
